oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Community Data Report, Clarksville and Montgomery County, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Report created by the Middle Tennessee Industrial Development Association with an overview of the Clarksville and Montgomery County community. The report includes a brief history of the area, population and climate statistics, summaries of existing amenities and industries, available natural resources, and sites available for development.
